### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7101
@customerId = {{CreateCustomer.response.body.data.id}}

### 1. Create Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "علی احمدی",
  "phoneNumber": "09123456789",
  "companyName": "شرکت نمونه",
  "isTemporary": false
}

### 2. Create Temporary Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "مشتری متفرقه",
  "phoneNumber": "09111111111",
  "isTemporary": true
}

### 3. Get Customer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Customers/{{customerId}}

### 4. Update Customer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Customers/{{customerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{customerId}}",
  "fullName": "علی احمدی (ویرایش شده)",
  "phoneNumber": "09123456789",
  "companyName": "شرکت جدید",
  "isTemporary": false
}

### 5. Get Paginated Customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Customers?page=1&pageSize=10

### 6. Get Paginated Customers with Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10,
  "filter": {
    "fullName": "علی",
    "isTemporary": false
  }
}

### 7. Delete Customer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Customers/{{customerId}}
